platform.summary: A general purpose Galaxy server Includes tools developped by [Dyliss](http://www.irisa.fr/dyliss/) and [GenScale](https://team.inria.fr/genscale/) bioinformatics research teams in Rennes, France.

quotas: You must be part of an academic research lab and create an account on [GenOuest](https://my.genouest.org).
The default quota for new users is 50GB.
